<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  
  <body>
       <center><h4> Your leave request has been approved </h4></center> 

   <p>Your leave request has been approved by <b><%= @from_manager.first_name.to_s+' '+@from_manager.last_name.to_s %></b> from date <b> <%= @leave_request.start_date.to_date %></b> to<b> <%= @leave_request.end_date.to_date%></b></p>
   <h4>Details of the Leave :-</h4>
   <p>Total Number of days :- <%= @leave_request.leave_count %></p>
   <p>Leave Reason :- <%= @leave_request.reason %></p>
   <h4>Requester Details :- <h4>
   <p>Employee ID :- <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:manual_employee_code) %></p>
   <p>Employee Name :- <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:first_name) %> <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:last_name) %></p>
  </body>
</html>